ice new medallion signature guarantee msg requirement see form for details      income made easy form use this form if you have an optional withdrawal benefit rider with an annuity contract and would like to enroll in john hancocks income made easy program new medallion signature guarantee msg requirement see form for details         investment option change form venture use this form to make investment option transfers in a venture series annuity on a onetime basis for new york contracts see form directly below     investment option change form venturenew york contracts only use this form to make investment option transfers in a venture series new york contract annuity on a onetime basis     required minimum distribution request form use this form to request that john hancock calculate and make a onetime withdrawal or schedule recurring automatic withdrawals from an annuity contract to satisfy an irs required minimum distribution rmd new medallion signature guarantee msg requirement see form for details            systematic withdrawal program form use this form to enroll in the systematic withdrawal program for an annuity product new medallion signature guarantee msg requirement see form for details         telephone withdrawal authorizationagreement form use this form to authorize withdrawals to be made over the telephone for the contract owners and the agent of record         third party authorization form use this form to authorize another person or entity to receive documents and information related to an individual annuity contract      trade authorization agreement form use this form to authorize contract owners andor an agent of record to make telephoneelectronic trades among various investment portfolios within a variable annuity contract          trust or entity ownership certification form use this form for trust or entity ownership changes examples include contracts owned by trusts partnerships corporations or charitable entities that are not issued in 